-M_WUdQbva1WUq_boXbP.text: Firefighters have received a report of a carbon monoxide tank bursting at Chipotle.

-M_WVBZeaTrWFM0fAewG.text: Firefighters are on the scene. They confirm nothing is showing from outside.

-M_WWUGmQOKvt-Vl09n7.text: Firefighters confirm that there is no hazard at the moment. The CO2 company has been reached.
